Package ar.edu.utn.frc.tup.lc.iv.services

Interface ExpenseService

All Known Implementing Classes:
ExpenseServiceImpl
@Service public interface ExpenseService
Service interface for managing expenses. This interface defines the business logic for expenses operations.
